{"tid":1910425,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"畜木界功能組別得150名登記選民，唔係放過佢嘛？","createTime":"2020-03-04T16:01:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-06T12:50:01.000Z","uid":230104,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"934ce92d9cc9c7a7798711709454b5744096624f","tid":1910425,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T16:01:40.000Z","msg":"漁農界功能界別是香港立法會選舉功能界別之一，前身乃1995年至1997年的漁農、礦產、能源及建造界，屬於當時的新九組之一，選民包括所有報稱從事漁農、礦產、能源或建造業議會的選民；主權移交後該界別改組為「漁農界」，選民資格僅限於政府指定的註冊漁農業團體。截至2018年登記選民人數僅為150"},{"pid":"0417bb534686d64fd3a52383d9670776ccb5a891","tid":1910425,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T16:02:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0yxdsau.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0yxdsau.png&h=ce09a826&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0ada0cc163f64e8d0f2808c36da26ca2abf13d85","tid":1910425,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T16:07:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QFWE7bW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQFWE7bW.png&h=c7ea14c9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MW21A5g.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMW21A5g.png&h=749f76a3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UWBauqh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUWBauqh.png&h=46c66acc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zQskRDE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzQskRDE.png&h=bba4b163&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TSyzV5k.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTSyzV5k.png&h=5a87dd92&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/78ULiiF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F78ULiiF.png&h=f10819eb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5WbNwDG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5WbNwDG.png&h=874b6056&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a7bdd025274dbbe3f8829e91e67ddec625cf1575","tid":1910425,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T16:08:40.000Z","msg":"首先混入去其中一個團體度成為會員，再登記成為選民"},{"pid":"2535b31be62155486b43ed86c83987fdb8e00c4e","tid":1910425,"uid":230104,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T16:11:41.000Z","msg":"對本地農業界稍有接觸的朋友，應會知道近十年除了上水農友黃七娣做主席的「香港新界本地農協會」，至少還有佘常光做主席的「有機農友會」、黃如榮做主席的「香港有機生活社」，以及「香港農業聯合會」。然而，農友完全不知道為何A會可以獲政府建議成為漁農界選民，B、C和D會則冇份。政制局長聶德權說，傳統功能組別並沒有明文的加入機制，但「有啲團體會寫信畀政府要求加入」，政府部門再「按行業情況」決定，標準不明。真正是官字兩把口，任佢噏。<br />\n<br />\n刪除團體的標準同樣飄忽。香港的漁農業早已息微，不少農會及漁會已沒有從事本業，但一日沒有取消團體或公司註冊，政府也不會主動調查是否仍然運作。<br />\n<br />\n對住呢個出晒名圍威喂功能組別，是否認真就輸？我打算邀請未成為選民的農會向政府自薦，也會嘗試舉報一些已經不再運作的農會漁會，看政府如何回應？有進展再跟大家報告。<br />\n<br />\n朱西迪"},{"pid":"5fbf1ebdc728bd1f36d90c4cfde47e1a3c6000ba","tid":1910425,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T16:13:42.000Z","msg":"連登仔關心kpop都唔出謀進攻功能組別"},{"pid":"cb8e92f68f155143b80823faed297df42aa6b043","tid":1910425,"uid":273703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T16:18:30.000Z","msg":"屋企有種花養貓組個興趣少爺小組 OK?"},{"pid":"f165912704f17c4552fbf1ea326c0c7345b607c9","tid":1910425,"uid":53612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T05:16:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a15e6281580cc0fc2daffab005edded8f98eea5e","tid":1910425,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T07:36:32.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"77e4135da47ac175361ab0a2543b841edf1d7288","tid":1910425,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cb8e92f68f155143b80823faed297df42aa6b043","tid":1910425,"uid":273703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T16:18:30.000Z","msg":"屋企有種花養貓組個興趣少爺小組 OK?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T07:36:55.000Z","msg":"如果一人租塊田仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\